message.body: Hey, sorry to be one of THOSE!! I actually just dropped the card in the mail, we'll be there with bells on!
Wonderful!!!!!! So happy to hear that!! :)
Hope your lesson today is great, can't wait to hear about it!
Oh also - would you mind giving $ a can of senior for lunch if you have time? We're trying 1 senior at a time so maybe he will waste less of it...
Thank you from a neurotic little tb!
